thread.title: BRIEF-Talanx FY Group Net Income Of Around EUR 670 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Talanx FY Group Net Income Of Around EUR 670 Million
text:
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Talanx AG:
* ACHIEVED GROUP NET INCOME OF AROUND EUR 670 (2016: 907) MILLION IN THE FINANCIAL YEAR 2017
* DIVIDEND PAYMENT AT LEAST EQUAL TO THE YEAR-EARLIER LEVEL IS ASSURED FROM TODAY’S PERSPECTIVE
* FY GROSS WRITTEN PREMIUMS GREW THROUGHOUT THE GROUP BY AROUND 6 PERCENT TO EUR 33.1 (31.1) BILLION‍​
* GROUP-WIDE NET LARGE LOSS BURDEN AMOUNTED TO EUR 1.6 (0.9) BLN‍​ Source text - bit.ly/2C0HGhh Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
